{
  "texts": [
    "However, this stringent demand is beyond the capabilities of existing vehicular communication or radar systems.",
    "Via implementing ISAC in V2X networks, both satisfactory sensing and communication performance can be guaranteed.Motivated by this, the researchers have dived into ISAC-enabled V2X networks from diverse aspects, such as waveform design [92], beamforming prediction [16,108], and target tracking [140].",
    "Specifically, Ma et al. [92] developed a signaling strategy based on IM for the multi-carrier FMCW radar, achieving the satisfactory sensing performance and higher communication rate.",
    "Moreover, Liu et al. [16] employed ISAC for both downlink communication and beam prediction, reducing the communication overhead significantly.",
    "Similarly, Yuan et al. [108] implemented ISAC at roadside units to achieve both information delivery and parameter estimation."
  ]
}